||Design Document - BeBetter||

|Below are the services we can make:|
1. user service: 
  a. This service will hold the details of the user.
  b. This service will have the logic for user authentication
  c. This service will have business logic for updating user profile
2. Task service: 
  a. This services will contain details of a task
  b. This service will have business logic for assign, complete or edit task attribute
  c. All other logic written in the requirement related to task details will be present inside this service 

